################################################################################
# FCGames — fluxo completo de ponta a ponta
#
# Use com a extensão "REST Client" (VS Code) ou o HTTP Client (Rider/IntelliJ).
# Clique em "Send Request" acima de cada bloco, NA ORDEM. O token e os IDs são
# referenciados automaticamente das respostas anteriores ({{login.response...}}),
# então você não precisa copiar nada.
#
# Pré-requisito: docker compose up (stack completa no ar).
# Acompanhe os efeitos em: docker compose logs -f notifications-worker
################################################################################

@users = http://localhost:5001
@catalog = http://localhost:5002
@payments = http://localhost:5003
@notifications = http://localhost:5004

### 1) Cadastra um usuário  -> dispara UsuarioCriadoEvento
# @name cadastro
POST {{users}}/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria",
  "email": "maria@teste.com",
  "senha": "Maria@123"
}

### 2) Login  -> retorna o token JWT
# @name login
POST {{users}}/usuarios/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "maria@teste.com",
  "senha": "Maria@123"
}

### 3) Lista os jogos (seed)  -> veja os IDs/precos retornados
# @name jogos
GET {{catalog}}/jogos
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### 4) COMPRA APROVADA (Hades 49,90)  -> 202 + orderId
#    Ajuste o indice [0] se Hades nao for o primeiro da lista em #3.
# @name compraAprovada
POST {{catalog}}/compras
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jogoId": "{{jogos.response.body.$[0].id}}"
}

### 5) COMPRA REJEITADA (Cyberpunk 2077 149,90 > 100)
#    Ajuste o indice [2] se Cyberpunk nao for o terceiro da lista em #3.
# @name compraRejeitada
POST {{catalog}}/compras
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jogoId": "{{jogos.response.body.$[2].id}}"
}

### 6) Consulta o pedido aprovado  (aguarde 1-2s apos #4 — processamento e assincrono)
#    Se o campo do id nao for "orderId", veja a resposta de #4 e ajuste.
GET {{catalog}}/compras/{{compraAprovada.response.body.$.orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### 7) Consulta o pagamento correspondente
GET {{payments}}/pagamentos/{{compraAprovada.response.body.$.orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

### 8) Biblioteca do usuario  -> deve conter Hades, nao conter Cyberpunk
GET {{catalog}}/biblioteca/{{cadastro.response.body.$.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.token}}

################################################################################
# Fluxo de Admin (jogos sao [Authorize Admin])
# Admin seedado: admin@fcgames.com / Admin@123
################################################################################

### Login do admin
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{users}}/usuarios/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@fcgames.com",
  "senha": "Admin@123"
}

### Cria um novo jogo (somente Admin)
POST {{catalog}}/jogos
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.$.token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Stardew Valley",
  "descricao": "Fazendinha relaxante",
  "preco": 24.90
}

################################################################################
# Health checks
################################################################################

### users
GET {{users}}/health

### catalog
GET {{catalog}}/health

### payments
GET {{payments}}/health

### notifications
GET {{notifications}}/health
